  "prompt": "What hotel in Varanasi would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "In Varanasi, as in many parts of India, finding a hotel that is accepting of unmarried couples can be challenging due to cultural sensitivities. However, several hotels and guesthouses are known to be more liberal and accommodating. Here are some tips and suggestions:\n\n### 1. **Book Reputable Hotels**\n   - **Luxury Hotels:** High-end hotels are generally more accommodating and professional. They tend to focus on guest privacy and are less likely to hassle unmarried couples.\n     - **BrijRama Palace** (Heritage Hotel)\n     - **Taj Ganges, Varanasi**\n     - **Radisson Hotel Varanasi**\n   - **Boutique Hotels:** These are often more flexible and understanding.\n     - **Hotel Surya**\n     - **Ganges View Guest House**\n\n### 2. **Check Oyo and Other Chains**\n   - **Oyo Rooms** and other similar chains often have options that are couple-friendly. Look for properties with high ratings and reviews specifically mentioning being couple-friendly.\n\n### 3. **Read Reviews**\n   - Platforms like **Booking.com**, **Agoda**, or **TripAdvisor** often have reviews from other unmarried couples. Look for comments about staff behavior and policies.\n\n### 4. **Call Ahead**\n   - Before booking, call the hotel to confirm their policy regarding unmarried couples. This can help avoid misunderstandings.\n\n### 5. **Airbnb**\n   - Many **Airbnb** hosts are open to renting to unmarried couples. Read reviews carefully and communicate with the host before booking.\n\n### 6. **Tips for a Smooth Stay**\n   - Carry valid ID proofs for both partners.\n   - Be respectful and discreet to avoid drawing unnecessary attention.\n   - Avoid overly budget or local guesthouses, which may be less accepting.\n\n### 7. **Local Recommendations**\n   - Some hotels known to be couple-friendly in Varanasi include:\n     - **Hotel Temple on Ganges**\n     - **Hotel Haifa**\n     - **Ganpati Guest House**\n\nAlways ensure you research thoroughly and confirm policies to have a hassle-free experience.",
